Apache2/AuthPAM
===============

Enable Apache mod_perl2 to use the Authen::PAM module for authentication.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Authen::PAM by Nikolay Pelov <nikip@iname.com>

